* OH, BOY, WILL YOU LINE

20:20.620 --> 20:23.523
[men answering chorus]

20:23.556 --> 20:26.293
* ME AND THE BABY
LIE IN THE SHADE *

20:26.326 --> 20:28.995
* THINK ABOUT THE MONEY
